OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1781628468
OL,3,CSinkhole repairs could take four more
OL,4,Cweeks
OL,6,FA main route into Dumfries will stay
OL,7,Fclosed for up to a further four weeks,
OL,8,Fdue to a sinkhole.
OL,10,FAnnan Road has been shut for several
OL,11,Fweeks already, while Scottish Water
OL,12,Frepairs a damaged section of sewer -
OL,13,Faround four metres below ground, which
OL,14,Fhas caused a sinkhole to appear.
OL,16,FThe sinkhole has affected local
OL,17,Fbusinesses, which say the closure of
OL,18,FAnnan Road has reduced passing trade.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1781628468
OL,3,CSinkhole repairs could take four more
OL,4,Cweeks
OL,6,FScottish Water, which is repairing the
OL,7,Fcrater, said the works could only be
OL,8,Fcarried out safely with a full road
OL,9,Fclosure, due to a damaged sewer about
OL,10,F4m (13ft) underground.
OL,12,FITV Border previously spoke to Abdul
OL,13,FMannan, who owns a convenience store
OL,14,Fdirectly in front of the road closure.
OL,16,FMr Mannan said: "It's having a big
OL,17,Fimpact, we are down nearly one third
OL,18,Fof our sales.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1781628468
OL,3,CSinkhole repairs could take four more
OL,4,Cweeks
OL,6,F"We've lost a lot of customers
OL,7,Fespecially in the morning time, we get
OL,8,Flots of lorry drivers, work men in the
OL,9,Fmorning and we are one third down.
OL,11,F"If I'm losing a few thousand pounds
OL,12,Fin a month time its going to impact on
OL,13,Fmy profit, and my overhead expenses
OL,14,Fare the same.
OL,16,F"I know they're doing their job, but
OL,17,Fwe have to do our job as well, and we
OL,18,Fare losing money as well."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1781628468
OL,3,CSinkhole repairs could take four more
OL,4,Cweeks
OL,6,FSince then, Scottish Water has
OL,7,Fconfirmed that it will need up to four
OL,8,Fmore weeks to fix the sinkhole.
OL,10,FA spokesperson said: "Work to repair
OL,11,Fthe damaged section of sewer
OL,12,Funderneath Annan Road in Dumfries is
OL,13,Funderway and we anticipate it will
OL,14,Ftake up to a further four weeks to
OL,15,Fcomplete.
OL,17,F"This is a technically challenging
OL,18,Frepair and the road closure will need
OL,19,Fto remain in place for the duration of
OL,20,Fthe works for the safety of the public
OL,21,Fand our operatives.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1781628468
OL,3,CSinkhole repairs could take four more
OL,4,Cweeks
OL,6,F"We understand that the closure is
OL,7,Fcausing disruption for customers and
OL,8,Froad users and we thank everyone
OL,9,Fimpacted for their patience,
OL,10,Funderstanding and cooperation.
OL,12,F"Further investigations are taking
OL,13,Fplace on the wider network locally in
OL,14,Forder to understand what, if any,
OL,15,Fadditional work will be required in
OL,16,Forder to maintain and improve the long-
OL,17,Fterm efficiency of the sewer network.
OL,18,FWe will update customers should any
OL,19,Ffurther work be required."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
